beer.beer_description:
Our brewers reckoned we’d need a truckload of hops to brew this IPA the right way. So we reached out to get the finest truckload of Australian and US hops for an IPA that doesn’t hold back. Big on aroma, clean present bitterness, and lasting fruits. Back it up, that’ll do.

HOPS
Centennial, Enigma, Vic Secret & Mosaic

MALT
Coopers Ale & Carapils
